snippet.title: First Teaser video | Typing Test on Steam | 2024 Q3
snippet.description:
Welcome to the ultimate typing challenge!
Compete against up to 50 players in an intense multiplayer experience that will test your speed and accuracy. With over 3 million words and 15 languages to choose from, every match is unique and exciting.

Track your progress with our scoring system and earn Steam achievements as you improve. Invite friends using our recommendation system and earn $0.5 for each successful invite. 

Join the competition now and prove you're the fastest typist!
